<figureCitation box="[159,252,980,1005]" captionStart="FIGURES 59 – 66" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1954,1976]" captionTargetBox="[187,1400,1438,1926]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[175,1411,1430,1932]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 59 – 66. Paramere of Metrocoris spp. (males) in external view. 59 – 62. M. sichuanensis Chen &amp; Nieser, 1993 (59: Qingchen mountain; 60: Laojun mountain; 61: Xinmin village; 62: Hubaoxia Forest Park); 63. M. astictus sp. nov.; 64. M. falciformis sp. nov.; 65. M. guizhouensis sp. nov.; 66. M. zhengi sp. nov.. Scale 0.2 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/269720/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="369">Figs. 63</figureCitation>
